      "levelSystemPrompt": "Answer the prompt with a maximum of 4 sentences. It should be a back-and-forth dialogue where each character speaks only once or twice.\n\nWhen the user includes multiple examples, mirror the tone, structure, and personality shown in those examples. Use the examples to guide the kind of humor, pacing, and relationship dynamic expected between the characters.\n\nAim for punchy, creative dialogue that captures the voice of each character. If the examples include callbacks, jokes, or specific emotional beats, match that level of depth in your response.\n\n",
